Body:
subscriber = Subscriber(aci='0.0.0.0 eth 0', ari='A.B.C', state=LineState.
    SHOWTIME, up=1024, down=2048, min_up=128, min_down=256, att_up=2040,
    att_down=4090, max_up=2048, max_down=4096, dsl_type=DslType.VDSL2,
    data_link=DataLink.ETHERNET, encap1=Encap1.UNTAGGED_ETHERNET, encap2=
    Encap2.EOAAL5_LLC_FCS)
len, tlvs = subscriber.tlvs
assert len == 3
assert struct.unpack_from('!HHI', tlvs, 36)[2] == DslType.VDSL2
assert struct.unpack_from('!HHI', tlvs, 52)[2] == LineState.SHOWTIME
assert struct.unpack_from('!HHI', tlvs, 60)[2] == 1024
assert struct.unpack_from('!HHI', tlvs, 68)[2] == 2048
assert struct.unpack_from('!HHI', tlvs, 76)[2] == 128
assert struct.unpack_from('!HHI', tlvs, 84)[2] == 256
assert struct.unpack_from('!HHI', tlvs, 92)[2] == 2040
assert struct.unpack_from('!HHI', tlvs, 100)[2] == 4090
assert struct.unpack_from('!HHI', tlvs, 108)[2] == 2048
assert struct.unpack_from('!HHI', tlvs, 116)[2] == 4096
